{"tid":2396292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Hong Kong Watch將與英國政府官員商討 探討港人於英國展開新生活可能會面對的困難及解決方法","createTime":"2021-02-05T12:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T01:31:44.000Z","uid":28114,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"61bbfcbd93f700e0f4038ab45c7bc556635108c5","tid":2396292,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Watch<br />\n🇬🇧 BN(O)政策線上分享會 &mdash;&mdash;「為何英國公民社會需要挺身幫助香港人」<br />\n<br />\n英國政府新推出的BN(O)政策於1月31日正式生效，預計有三十萬合資格的香港人將透過相關計劃移居到英國生活及工作。但在異地展開新生活難關重重，除了政府部門之外，公民社會也將在協助香港人融入到當地社會的過程中起到關鍵作用。<br />\n<br />\n香港監察將於英國當地非牟利組織 UK Welcomes Refugee 聯合舉辦線上分享會，與公民團體代表及政府官員就「公民組織應如何創造友好的環境迎接新抵埗的香港人」作出討論，探討香港人於英國展開新生活可能會面對的困難以及解決方法等等。<br />\n<br />\n👉 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/UkWelcomes/status/1355197399338258438?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUkWelcomes%2Fstatus%2F1355197399338258438%3Fs%3D20&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=fe8ec7b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUkWelcomes%2Fstatus%2F1355197399338258438%3Fs%3D20&h=ba407d48\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/UkWelcomes/status/1355197399338258438?s=20</a><br />\n <br />\n🕰 時間 TIME<br />\n11/02/2021（Thursday）<br />\n7pm 香港時間 HKT | 6am EST | 11am GMT<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1457138397739962/posts/3589826731137774/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1457138397739962%2Fposts%2F3589826731137774%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=40afc40b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1457138397739962/posts/3589826731137774/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"73734120ba8fcb762fdaa8e3341cd669f63e9a5a","tid":2396292,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"當BNO係Refugees?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a239161b5566d100a9acd9e5f685b1bc07